comments: She\'s the best! Extremely approachable and always cheerful! She\'ll help you with anything - whether it deals with her class or not. One of the best profs I\'ve ever had!

Grace is the nicest, most caring professor I\'ve had at K-State. She absolutely cares about her students and doesn\'t put herself on a pedestal. I took another class from her this semester because she is so wonderful. HIGHLY recommend her :)
